instruction: Create a fictional character’s monologue introducing themselves.
output: Hi, I'm Annabelle! I'm a twenty-nine year old librarian from the Midwest who loves nothing more than collecting books and telling stories. I have a passion for history and literature, and strive to bring these stories to life. I'm a bit of an introvert, but when I'm with my closest friends, I'm the life of the party. I'm also an avid traveler, exploring the world and learning new cultures whenever I get the chance.
